#Online Polling System
The Online Polling System is a web-based platform designed to facilitate the creation, management, and participation in polls and surveys. This system allows users to quickly and efficiently gather opinions from a wide audience, making it ideal for elections, feedback collection, and decision-making processes.

Key Features:
User Authentication: Secure login system to ensure that only authorized users can create and participate in polls.
Poll Creation and Management: Easy-to-use interface for setting up polls, defining options, and managing ongoing surveys.
Real-Time Voting: Participants can cast their votes in real-time, with immediate updates to poll results.
Result Visualization: Instant display of poll results through charts and graphs, offering clear insights into voting trends.
Data Security: Robust measures to ensure the integrity of the voting process, preventing duplicate votes and unauthorized access.
Responsive Design: Accessible on various devices, including desktops, tablets, and smartphones.
This system streamlines the process of collecting and analyzing public opinions, providing a reliable and user-friendly tool for a variety of applications.
